title: Support Main looking for club / duos
body:
Hey guys,


Support main here looking for a club to join / duos / ranked 5's  to play with in solo queue. 
Have been Gold in the past, haven't played much the last couple of seasons due to toaster of a computer shitting the bed, but looking to play a lot more now. Have discord etc. Not a rager so no need to worry about getting flamed. 

Currently silver (still in promos). 

In-game ID is Mooofish - hit me up :)
